                     <interp inst="t18591024-975-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>, Stealing 1 watch, value 6<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. of <persName id="t18591024-name-437" type="victimName">
